Casein kinase substrate phosphorylations

Bing Shui

2021-10-11

Library Preparation

library(tidyverse)
library(RColorBrewer)
library(gplots)
library(knitr)
library(mosaic)

Objective

To investigate the phosphorylation status of members of the casein kinase families and select substrates unique to Csnk2a1 for WB validation.

Casein kinase family members examined here: - Csnk1a1 (CK1A) - Csnk1d (CK1D) - Csnk1e (CK1E) - Csnk2a1 (CK2A1) - Csnk2a2 (CK2A2) - Csnk2b (CK2B)

Unscaled and scaled (to total protein change) phosphorylation status will be examined.

Analysis

Set up function

phospho_target_info <- function(kinase, all_height=12, sig_height=10) {
  # all target info
  target <- k.s.list %>% select(kinase) %>% na.omit() %>% unlist()
  target_phospho <- phos_prot %>% filter(site_id %in% target)
  target_phospho <- inner_join(target_phospho, total_prot[,c(2,7)], by = c("Protein Id" = "Protein Id"))
  target_phospho_quant <- phos_prot_quant %>% filter(site_id %in% target_phospho$site_id)
  colnames(target_phospho)[c(10,13)] <- c("Phospho_LFC", "Protein_LFC")
  target_phospho$scaled_phospho_LFC <- target_phospho$Phospho_LFC - target_phospho$Protein_LFC
  target_phospho <- inner_join(target_phospho, substrate_freq, by = c("site_id" = "substrate_list"))
  if(dim(target_phospho)[1]> 0) {
    filename <- paste("CK_Target/", kinase, "_target_phosphorylations.csv", sep = "")
    write_csv(target_phospho, filename)
  }
 
  # Significant target phosphosite info (p < 0.05)
  sig_target_phospho <- target_phospho %>% filter(p_values <= 0.05)
  sig_target_phospho_quant <- target_phospho_quant %>% filter(site_id %in% sig_target_phospho$site_id)
  print(paste("Number of significantly changed target phosphorylations of ", kinase, ": ", dim(sig_target_phospho)[1], sep = ""))
  
  if (dim(sig_target_phospho)[1] > 0) {
    filename <- paste("CK_Target/", kinase, "_sig_target_phosphorylations.csv", sep = "")
    write_csv(sig_target_phospho, filename)
  }
  # Heatmap of all targets (unscaled and scaled)
  my_palette <- colorRampPalette(c("blue", "white", "red"))(100)
  if (dim(target_phospho)[1] > 1) {
    # LFC heatmap
    heatmap_matrix <- as.matrix(target_phospho[,c(10,14)])
    rownames(heatmap_matrix) <- target_phospho$name_id
    figure_name <- paste("CK_Target/", kinase, "_target_phosphorylations_LFC.pdf", sep = "")
    pdf(figure_name,
        width = 8,
        height = all_height)
    par(cex.main=1.1)
    heatmap.2(heatmap_matrix,
              main = paste(kinase, "target phosphorylations LFC"),
              density.info = "none",
              key = TRUE,
              lwid = c(3,7),
              lhei = c(1,7),
              col=my_palette,
              margins = c(16,10),
              symbreaks = TRUE,
              breaks=seq(-2,2,0.04),
              trace = "none",
              dendrogram = "row",
              labRow = rownames(heatmap_matrix),
              cexCol = 1.5,
              Colv = "NA")
    dev.off()
    
    # Quantification heatmap
    heatmap_matrix <- as.matrix(target_phospho_quant[, c(6:15)])
    heatmap_matrix <- t(apply(heatmap_matrix, 1, zscore))
    rownames(heatmap_matrix) <- target_phospho_quant$name_id
    figure_name <- paste("CK_Target/", kinase, "_target_phosphorylations_quant.pdf", sep = "")
    pdf(figure_name,
        width = 8,
        height = all_height)
    par(cex.main=1.1)
    heatmap.2(heatmap_matrix,
              main = paste(kinase, "target phosphorylations Quant"),
              density.info = "none",
              key = TRUE,
              lwid = c(3,7),
              lhei = c(1,7),
              col=my_palette,
              margins = c(16,10),
              symbreaks = TRUE,
              trace = "none",
              dendrogram = "row",
              labRow = rownames(heatmap_matrix),
              cexCol = 1.5,
              Colv = "NA")
    dev.off()
  }
  
  # Heatmap of significant targets (unscaled and scaled)
  if (dim(sig_target_phospho)[1] > 1) {
    # Sig LFC heatmap
    heatmap_matrix <- as.matrix(sig_target_phospho[,c(10,14)])
    rownames(heatmap_matrix) <- sig_target_phospho$name_id
    figure_name <- paste("CK_Target/", kinase, "_sig_target_phosphorylations_LFC.pdf", sep = "")
    pdf(figure_name,
        width = 8,
        height = sig_height)
    par(cex.main=1.1)
    heatmap.2(heatmap_matrix,
              main = paste(kinase, "sig target phosphorylations LFC"),
              density.info = "none",
              key = TRUE,
              lwid = c(3,7),
              lhei = c(1,7),
              col=my_palette,
              margins = c(16,10),
              symbreaks = TRUE,
              breaks=seq(-2,2,0.04),
              trace = "none",
              dendrogram = "row",
              labRow = rownames(heatmap_matrix),
              cexCol = 1.5,
              Colv = "NA")
    dev.off()
    
    # Sig Quantification heatmap
    heatmap_matrix <- as.matrix(sig_target_phospho_quant[, c(6:15)])
    heatmap_matrix <- t(apply(heatmap_matrix, 1, zscore))
    rownames(heatmap_matrix) <- sig_target_phospho_quant$name_id
    figure_name <- paste("CK_Target/", kinase, "_sig_target_phosphorylations_quant.pdf", sep = "")
    pdf(figure_name,
        width = 8,
        height = sig_height)
    par(cex.main=1.1)
    heatmap.2(heatmap_matrix,
              main = paste(kinase, "sig target phosphorylations Quant"),
              density.info = "none",
              key = TRUE,
              lwid = c(3,7),
              lhei = c(1,7),
              col=my_palette,
              margins = c(16,10),
              symbreaks = TRUE,
              trace = "none",
              dendrogram = "row",
              labRow = rownames(heatmap_matrix),
              cexCol = 1.5,
              Colv = "NA")
    dev.off()
  }
}
